3 Gréat and wóndrous are your wórks,
O Lórd, Almíghty Gód!
Júst and trúe are your wáys,
O Kíng of the nátions!

4 Whó would not féar, O Lord,
and glórify your náme?

For you alóne are the Hóly One,
for all nátions will cóme,
and théy will wórship befóre you,
for your ríghteous déeds have been revéaled.
